ore, outpour,"},{"s":18.66,"e":19.52,"text":"Mercy more, through every door."},{"s":20.58,"e":24.86,"text":"Light ignite, make fear take flight,"},{"s":24.86,"e":27.82,"text":"Brightest white, through darkest night."},{"s":28.54,"e":31.4,"text":"Peace release, let panic cease,"},{"s":31.4,"e":34.9,"text":"Grace increase, bring sacred peace."},{"s":34.9,"e":38.42,"text":"Heal, reveal, make whole, make real,"},{"s":38.42,"e":42.02,"text":"Seal my soul with holy steel."},{"s":42.02,"e":45.34,"text":"Guide my mind, unwind, be kind,"},{"s":45.34,"e":48.84,"text":"Leave no fear or lie behind."},{"s":48.84,"e":52.36,"text":"Calm my chest, grant rest, bless best,"},{"s":52.36,"e":56.14,"text":"Lift this weight from heart and breast."},{"s":56.14,"e":59.22,"text":"Angels stand, hand in hand,"},{"s":59.22,"e":62.96,"text":"Guard this land, by Your command."},{"s":62.96,"e":65.74,"text":"Saints arise, wise skies, kind eyes,"},{"s":65.74,"e":70,"text":"Shield my soul from fear and lies."},{"s":70,"e":72.66,"text":"Pain drain, chain slain, rain gain,"},{"s":72.66,"e":76.1,"text":"Wash my brain from strain and stain."},{"s":76.1,"e":78.84,"text":"Night bright, fight right, sight light,"},{"s":78.84,"e":83.96,"text":"Turn my fright to faith tonight."},{"s":97.52,"e":101.34,"text":"Jesus near, clear fear, steer here,"},{"s":101.34,"e":104.7,"text":"Hold me dear, appear sincere."},{"s":104.7,"e":108.3,"text":"Love above, dove-glove, shove none,"},{"s":108.3,"e":111.74,"text":"Pull me close to Christ the Son."},{"s":111.74,"e":114.9,"text":"Grace embrace, replace disgrace,"},{"s":115.36,"e":118.38,"text":"Make my heart a holy place."},{"s":118.38,"e":121.8,"text":"Breath by breath, undo death,"},{"s":121.8,"e":125.7,"text":"Give me life with every breath."},{"s":125.7,"e":129.6,"text":"Amen, amen, again, again,"},{"s":129.6,"e":132.62,"text":"Heal my spirit, heart, and brain."},{"s":132.62,"e":135.94,"text":"Peace remain, break every chain,"},{"s":135.94,"e":142.84,"text":"Let Your holy love reign."}],"duration":162.28,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-25T06:38:40.309Z","stats":{"whisperWords":216,"polishedWords":181,"matched":157,"matchRate":0.867}}